{"lastModified":1773328579569,"uri":"c::7579706445::vessel::396e62f0-43b2-11ef-b3ab-f3f0ef91fbca","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nStep aboard the distinguished Ferretti 830 LIDIA, an exquisite Italian vessel launched in 2006 and meticulously refitted in 2023, boasting a length of 25.3 meters (83 feet).\n\nThis prestigious yacht invites you to an unparalleled cruising experience, accommodating up to 8 guests in absolute luxury, overseen by a dedicated and professional crew of 4.\n\nAs we enter, the interior offers a harmonious flow adorned with sumptuous leather furnishings in an inviting cream hue and the port side is equipped in a way that makes it ideal for relaxation while the formal dining area is bathed in natural light from panoramic windows. The exterior living spaces are generous and elegantly design with a shaded aft deck that invites you to dine alfresco or unwind with a cocktail enjoying breathtaking views.\n\nFurther aft, you will find a toy garage that reveals a teak beach for effortless access to the water while the expansive sunpad on the foredeck will offer you total privacy. The accommodation on the Ferretti 830 is designed with utmost comfort in mind featuring luxurious en-suite cabins, ports for natural light and TVs. The magnificent yacht provides aquatic entertainment options with an array of water toys and snorkeling equipment for those who seek some more adventure!\n\nIf you are looking for the ultimate cruising experience on the Aegean Sea, LIDIA stands out for her unparalleled comfort and privacy. Embark on a journey of opulence and tranquility, where every detail is crafted to elevate your yachting experience to new heights!","blueprint":{"name":"LIDIA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::396e62f0-43b2-11ef-b3ab-f3f0ef91fbca::assets::dd2c5051-d5d3-11f0-be93-8b88fe7c6d0e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::396e62f0-43b2-11ef-b3ab-f3f0ef91fbca::assets::dd309610-d5d3-11f0-9719-299b6b3ae587/{im